snippet.title: Technical Sagar
snippet.description:
My name is Abhishek Sagar and I am a self-taught white hat hacker and a commerce graduate from India, Currently working for some well known international brands. Internet and Ethical Hacking is my passion and i believe in helping people with my abilities and knowledge base. I am learning these things from last 13 years and it feels like learning is a part of my life now. I am running this channel for my community where i teach technical things in my mother tongue "Hindi" which makes this experience even more interesting. 

Have a nice stay here!

For Business Enquiries Mail Me At: sagarwebsol@gmail.com

I do not provide tech support over e-mail.

Thank you
